 specially historical\\\\medieval ones , and you think you are smart enough to build and manage a desert castle, yesbuy it. But if you think you can learn everything in the game and become an OP player in it in 2 hours , thendon’t buy it.There are allot of videos and guides there you can watch or read to learn how to have strong economy and military power.A good video.Don’t look at the reviews percentage on steam store page , most of them are 1 lined review with no reasonable dislike. However, don’t buy this game unless it\\\'s on sales it gets really cheap, otherwise it’s too expensive and doesn’t really deserve its original price without sales.One more thing , don’t buy the special edition , it really adds silly things for nothing.The game is very addictive and you will enjoy it.Thank you for reading!My funny artworks xD.http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=695210566http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=695243240"
