ope. To run the economy, you simply horde a diverse array of resources and use them the exact same every time.This game manages to add on the mistakes of previous games and then adds more issues by trying to squeeze almost the exact same sort of format into a 3D engine with some additional features that only serve to frustrate by adding to the amount of micromanaging required. Do yourself a favor and don't waste money on this game till it finally ends up where it's destined, the 5$ bin."
